name: Yvette de Koning
position 2: Mentor for Actuarial Practice Cycle Students
summary:
My name is Yvette de Koning and I have been working for EY since 2015. Currently I am working as a Manager within the Dutch Actuarial practice, focusing on the Non-Life and the Health sector. I have experience within Actuarial and Financial Services serving large multinational insurance companies, mid market and large local and international companies, pension funds and banks. 
I am a member of the Dutch Actuarial Association and a teacher in the actuarial post master at the Universiteit van Amsterdam where I coach students in their personal development focusing on their career and personal well-being.
Another passion besides my work is cycling. I participate in road races and beach races.

name: Jamie Berkhout
summary: Bij PwC geloven wij dat je uitdagingen beter samen kunt aanpakken. Daarom bouwen wij aan diverse, ambitieuze teams, waarin je wordt uitgedaagd je hart en je waarden te volgen.
